data.description: **Hardwood floors to be contracted to be redone prior to move in.**  This 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom home is nestled in the heart of a beautiful, mature neighborhood. Enjoy the convenience of living in the middle of town while still enjoying the peace and quiet of a well-established community close to shopping and main roads. Recently updated with fresh paint throughout, AC serviced 2023. The upper-level features one full bathroom 3 bedrooms, while the basement provides a half bath and 1 bedroom with a BONUS additional nonconforming flex room or office space. New LVP flooring installed in basement and bathrooms. This charming home is perfect for entertaining or simply relaxing in your new home. Don't miss out on this incredible opportunity to make this house your new home!
